(Paillier Properties) show newline
(-------------------) show newline
() show newline
() show newline
(    ;; Additive homomorphism) show newline
(    \(= \(decrypt \(he-add \(encrypt a\) \(encrypt b\)\)\)) show newline
(       \(+ a b\)\)) show newline
(    ;; Scalar multiplication via repeated addition) show newline
(    \(= \(decrypt \(he-scalar-mult \(encrypt a\) k\)\)) show newline
(       \(* a k\)\)) show newline
(    ;; Semantic security - ciphertexts indistinguishable) show newline
(    \(not \(distinguishable? \(encrypt 0\) \(encrypt 1\)\)\)) show newline
